// String utility surface for example fileins.
//
// The current implementation intentionally keeps this file thin. The runtime
// provides only low-level pieces needed by examples:
//
//   string_len(text)
//   string_chars(text)
//   string_slice(text, start, end)
//   string_from_chars(chars)
//   lower(text)
//
// Higher-level parsing policy should live in Mica source, not in Rust
// transports.
